title: Remove Maintenance API Calls from Object Screen
description: |
  Remove or disable the maintenance API calls that are not needed for the object screen:
  - Remove maintenance API endpoints from API client if only used in object screen
  - Remove maintenance data fetching hooks/components from object screen
  - Clean up any related state management for maintenance data
  - Ensure no regressions in object screen core functionality

acceptance:
  - Maintenance API calls no longer appear in network tab on object screen
  - Object screen loads and functions normally without maintenance data
  - No TypeScript errors after removal
  - Object list displays correctly without maintenance info

requires: []
estimated: 4 hours
